    <item>
      <title>债务缠身的老挝选择延期还款，因为还款金额几乎翻倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/debt-saddled-laos-turns-to-deferrals-as-repayments-nearly-double</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据政府报告显示，老挝去年的外债偿还额几乎翻了一番，达到 9.5 亿美元，这促使这个东南亚国家寻求额外的延期偿还，以避免拖欠超过经济产出的债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/debt-saddled-laos-turns-to-deferrals-as-repayments-nearly-double</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 05:25:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡房价再次上涨，不受销售放缓的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/singapore-home-prices-rise-again-defying-sales-slowdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡房价连续第四个季度上涨，因为该国房地产估值继续抵抗销售大幅放缓的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/singapore-home-prices-rise-again-defying-sales-slowdown</guid>
